---
title: Cheesy Chicken & Spiced Black Beans with Cilantro, Smoky Red Pepper Crema & Garlic Bread
description: Weeknights feeling busier and more jam-packed than ever? We hear you! That’s why we’re bringing you our quickest, easiest meals yet. Introducing Oven-Ready Dinners. All you have to do is assemble in our aluminum trays, pop ’em in the oven, and dig in! No need to worry about prep or dirtying multiple dishes. This week, we’re featuring saucy black beans and cheesy spiced chicken, all dolloped with smoky red pepper crema and served with garlic bread for dunking. You can have all that on the table in just 30 minutes! Now that’s a weeknight win.
